  %body

    .pure-g

      .pure-u-1
        .header

          .pure-u-1-3
            %h1 Product Science

          .pure-u-1-2
            %ul.pure-menu.pure-menu-horizontal
              %li
                =link_to 'Home', '/'
              %li
                =link_to 'Services', '#services'
              %li
                =link_to 'Team', '#team'
              %li
                =link_to 'Contact', '#contact'

      .pure-u-1
        #hero

          %img.pure-img{ src:"/images/wind-turbine-road-2x.jpg" }

          %div.tagline
            %h2 Cleanweb Product Development
            %h3 We build digital products to help people solving environmental and social problems.
            %h3 If that sounds like you, we’re here to help you get where you need to be.

      .pure-u-1

        #services

          .pure-g

            .pure-u-1

              .l-box
                %h2 Services

          .pure-g

            .pure-u-1-1.pure-u-lg-1-3

              .user-research.l-box
                %h3 User research and content strategy
                %p Understand who your users are, and how your site is being used. We help you with user testing, making sense of your web stats, and keeping your content concise and relevant to your audience.

            .pure-u-1-1.pure-u-lg-1-3

              .development.l-box
                %h3 Development
                %p We build accessible, elegant, usable sites and web applications with open source software, and agile development practices. We specialise in using Django, Ruby on Rails, and Wordpress.

            .pure-u-1-1.pure-u-lg-1-3
              .hosting.l-box
                %h3 Hosting
                %p Rest easy with your sites running on secure, reliable, flexible cloud hosting, powered by planet friendly, clean energy.

